cause as big a catastrophe 
two key differences the mega borgs cargo was light crude 
which disperses much more rapidly than the heavy crude carried by 
the exxon valdez and fire is consuming the mega borgs oil 
the exxon valdez spilled nearly 11 million gallons of oil 
about onefifth of the 987foot ships cargo when it ran aground 
