sources all of whom spoke on condition of anonymity 
right now he feels this is the best he can get one source 
said it guarantees him nothing but there is a hope that if he 
isnt running again stephens might reconsider his stance 
the sources said barry has agonized over the decision to abandon 
hopes of retaining the job he has held since 1979 
anything is possible one source said hes getting a lot 
of pressure from his supporters not to do this and right now hes 
waking up every morning and deciding what he wants to do 
